extendedInfo.description: If you are Cary Brothers's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Cary Brothers's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Cary Brothers's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Cary Brothers's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)************************Main Features ************************- Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics************************List of albums ************************- Who You Are- Under Control************************List of lyrics ************************- After The Fall- Alien- All The Rage- Belong- Blue Eyes- Break Off The Bough- Can't Take My Eyes Off You- Forget About You- Ghost Town- Honestly- If You Were Here- Jealousy- Loneliest Girl In The World- Over & Out- Precious Lie- Ride- Skyway- Someday- Something About You- The Glass Parade- The Last One- Think Awhile- Under Control- Who You Are
